name: Antlers print inverted version
description:
An unframed print of a drawing I did, inspired by my interest in animal bones and their skeletal systems, combined with my interest in nature. 

Drawing originally rendered in micron pens, then was inverted in Photoshop.

Print is surrounded by a 1" border. Can be printed glossy or matte, please specify which. Drawing is about 6" wide by 8" tall, with border included (without border, 4" wide by 6" tall).

Shipped in a bubble wrap envelope to protect the item(s).
